// 本番環境構成例

| functions                  | AWS Service        
| -------------------------- | -------------------
| Frontend(Next.js Static)   | S3 + CloudFront    
| Backend(FastAPI)           | ECS Fargate        
| DB(MySQL)                  | Lightsail DB       
| Docker Image Management    | ECR                
| HTTPS / CDN                | CloudFront + ACM   
| Secrets                    | SSM Parameter Store

